{
  "texts": [
    "In the second paper (Rasmy et al. 2021), clinical experts were involved to verify the reliability of the semantic relations between diseases identified by the models.",
    "Apart from these simple cases, none of the approaches were adopted or presented follow-up papers that show the application or validations of the proposals in real scenarios.",
    "Indeed, Table 4 suggests that performance comparisons are only conducted using other computational approaches.",
    "This inexistence of such advanced evaluation processes may be associated with the need for regulations, as discussed in the previous comments.",
    "In other words, the technology transition from academia to the market requires well-defined regulatory compliances to guide such a process."
  ]
}